 28→/// `SystemInfoService` implementation backed by the gateway's live state.
 29→///
 30→/// Covers methods that read gateway-internal data (connections, nodes, hooks,
 31→/// heartbeat) rather than delegating to a domain service crate.
 32→pub struct GatewaySystemInfoService {
