 36→/// GraphQL chat shim that resolves the live chat service at call time.
 37→///
 38→/// GraphQL schema construction happens before the late-bound chat service is
 39→/// attached. Resolving through `GatewayState::chat()` keeps GraphQL aligned
 40→/// with RPC/WebSocket behavior after the override is installed.
 41→pub struct GraphqlChatServiceProxy {
 42→    pub state: Arc<GatewayState>,
 43→}
